{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"24":"Wages (Kitab Al-Ijarah)"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3550,"arabicnumber":3550,"text":"حدثنا موسى بن إسماعيل، حدثنا أبان، عن يحيى، عن أبي سلمة، عن جابر، أن نبي الله صلى الله عليه وسلم كان يقول ‏ \"‏ العمرى لمن وهبت له ‏\"‏ ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari And Sahih Muslim"}],"reference":{"book":24,"hadith":135}}]}